content: <rdf:RDF xmlns:foaf="http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/" xmlns:owl="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#" xmlns:rdfs="http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#" xmlns:rdf="http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#" xmlns:dcat="http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#" xmlns:dct="http://purl.org/dc/terms/">   <dcat:Dataset rdf:about="http://data.opencolorado.org/dataset/drcog-2012-acs-5-year-survey-metadata">     <owl:sameAs rdf:resource="urn:uuid:a809dfb1-4c8b-4fb5-a339-44bc03d7d55f"></owl:sameAs>     <dct:description>Description of Attributes from every table available for download from DRCOG for the 2012 ACS 5 Year Survey.   This includes the Block Group level table, the Place level table, and two Tract level tables.  All data includes the entire state of Colorado.  This spreadsheet indicates what downloadable .csv table each census table (indicated by \ufffd\ufffd\ufffdDRCOG Table\ufffd\ufffd\ufffd) is a part of.  In the.csv files each field is indicated by the Table ID number and the Line number you see in the metadata spreadsheet.  For example, if the Table Id is B01001 and the Line number is 1 in this metadata spreadsheet, then the field number will look like B01001_1 in the .csv file.  NOTE: When importing the .csv files into a Database, the software may try to turn the geoid field into a number field, which will drop the first 0 from the census code and will make the table not linkable to the geographies. Whatever software you use to import the table, you will want to make sure that field gets imported as a string or text field.</dct:description>     <foaf:homepage rdf:resource="http://data.opencolorado.org/dataset/drcog-2012-acs-5-year-survey-metadata"></foaf:homepage>     <rdfs:label>drcog-2012-acs-5-year-survey-metadata</rdfs:label>     <dct:identifier>drcog-2012-acs-5-year-survey-metadata</dct:identifier>     <dct:title>DRCOG:           2012 ACS 5 Year Survey Metadata        </dct:title>         <dcat:distribution>             <dcat:Distribution>                 <dcat:accessURL rdf:resource="http://gis.drcog.org/datacatalog/sites/default/files/ACS_2012_5YR_METADATA.xlsx"></dcat:accessURL>                     <dct:format>                         <dct:IMT>                             <rdf:value>XLS</rdf:value>                             <rdfs:label>XLS</rdfs:label>                         </dct:IMT>                     </dct:format>                <dct:title>ACS_2012_5YR_METADATA.xlsx</dct:title>             </dcat:Distribution>         </dcat:distribution>     <dct:creator>       <rdf:Description>         <foaf:name>DRCOG</foaf:name>         <foaf:mbox rdf:resource="mailto:"></foaf:mbox>       </rdf:Description>     </dct:creator>     <dct:contributor>       <rdf:Description>         <foaf:name>DRCOG Geospatial Team</foaf:name>         <foaf:mbox rdf:resource="mailto:geospatial@drcog.org"></foaf:mbox>       </rdf:Description>     </dct:contributor>     <dct:rights rdf:resource="http://www.opendefinition.org/licenses/cc-by"></dct:rights>   </dcat:Dataset> </rdf:RDF>
